miscConds.notes: Restitution to be paid as a condition of probation to the following:  $2,295.95 to Target and $1,947.00 to Walmart.  Restitution to be paid before costs or fines.

Submit to an AODA assessment, follow through with any treatment recommended.  No use or possession of alcohol, controlled substances or drug paraphernalia. Comply with random urine screens.  Maintain absolute sobriety. Inform Agent of all prescriptions.  Valid prescriptions only with prior agent approval and to be taken only in the manner they are ordered.

No contact with Target, Walmart and Game Stop Stores listed in the criminal complaint and read-in list.  Maintain employment and/or combination of schooling.
  If probation is revoked and a prison term is not ordered, or if probation is discharged/terminated, a civil judgment shall be entered against the defendant and in favor of restitution victims and government entities for outstanding financial obligations.  Collection may include income assignment.
